At boot prompt enter corepure64 followed by one or more space seperated options:

 noraid                     Skip RAID
 tz=CST-8                   Timezone
 console=tty0               Serial port consoles
 waitusb=10                 Wait 10 seconds for slow USB devices
 base                       Do not load any extensions.
 noembed                    Unpack initramfs to tmpfs
 norestore                  Turn off the automatic restore
 noswap                     Do not use swap partition
